Class SurvivalSlimefunGuide

java.lang.Object
io.github.thebusybiscuit.slimefun4.implementation.guide.SurvivalSlimefunGuide
All Implemented Interfaces:
SlimefunGuideImplementation
Direct Known Subclasses:
CheatSheetSlimefunGuide
public class SurvivalSlimefunGuide extends Object implements SlimefunGuideImplementation
The SurvivalSlimefunGuide is the standard version of our SlimefunGuide. It uses an Inventory to display SlimefunGuide contents.
